	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=251613><span id= >BlackIslandRose</span></a><br><span id=notbold>39 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>On Prexus server, the mallet and anvil are NoDrop. We can't intentionally drop them from our inventory, but they can remain behind after performing combines in the forge. The problem is the same.<br><br>When you lose your tools, you only have two options:<br>1) Petition a GM.<br>2) Redo the quest to obtain the tools.<br><br>I've read that it's usually easier just to redo the quest to obtain the tools again. Looking forward to obtaining a set of my own to start shadowscream armor in the next month or so.<br></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Piedmont Meandre<br>Prexus server<br>Enchanter of Erud<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=999180" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=999180</a></td></tr>
